high_descs: Turn right and go around to the other side of the white table.
Pick up the gray knife on the table.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn left and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the middle shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the right side of the white table with the sliced bread.
Pick up one slice of the bread from the table.
Turn left and go back to the refrigerator.
Remove the bread after cooling on the top shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the left side of the white table.
Place the bread on the table. towards the front edge.

high_descs: Turn right, head around the stool to the left and walk to the side of the white table on the left.
Pick up the knife in front of the loaf of bread on the table.
Slice the loaf of bread in the middle of the table.
Turn left, hang a right to the wall and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Place the knife on the middle shelf to let it chill inside the fridge and close the door.
Turn left, hang a left at the counter and walk to the side of the white table on the left.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf on the table.
Turn left, hang a right to the wall and walk to the fridge on the left.
Put the slice of bread inside the fridge on the top shelf to the left of the white mug, let it chill, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the side of the white table on the right.
Place the chilled slice of bread on the right corner of the table in front of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Chill a knife and place a slice of chilled bread on a table.
